    "en": {
      "title": "\"Ruhunu Kumari\" was derailed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Railway Department has announced that the \"Ruhunu Kumari\" train has derailed this morning in Galle-Bussa section.",
        "Railway Transport Superintendent Kamini Senaviratne said that the coastal train service has been completely affected due to this.",
        "In this situation, it is reported that the work of tracking the said train is being carried out quickly. (R)"
      ],
